                     <title xml:lang="he-Latn-x-lc">Ya᾿ir nativ</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he">יאיר נתיב</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <note>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>An anonymous Hebrew translation of the 'Viaticum' of Constantinus Africanus, itself a free rendering, in a shortened form, of Ibn Gazzar's 'Zād al-musāfir wa-qūt al-ḥāḍir'. The title 'Ya᾿ir nativ' is written on the top of the first page, but the missing first leaf of the first quire perhaps contained a fuller title. </p>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>The second section begins on folio 22r, the third on folio 37v, the fourth on folio 59r, the fifth on folio 84r, the sixth on folio 114v, and the seventh on folio 130r. </p>
                     
                     
                     
                     </note>
                  
                  
                  
                  </msItem>
                  
                  
                  
                  <msItem rend="">
                     
                     
                     
                     <locus from="159v" to="171v"/>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he-Latn-x-lc">Sefer ha-ma῾alot</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he">ספר המעלות</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <author>
                        
                        
                        
                        <persName key="viaf.org/viaf/74653052" xml:lang="en">Ibn al-Gazzar, Aḥmad ibn Ibrahim, 932-1009</persName>
                        
                        
                        
                        <persName key="viaf.org/viaf/74653052" xml:lang="he">ג'זאר, אחמד בן אבראהים אבן</persName>
                     
                     
                     
                     </author>
                     
                     
                     
                     <note>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>An anonymous Hebrew translation, based on Latin version, of Ibn Gazzar's work, preceded by a short introduction and enumeration of chapters. </p>
                     
                     
                     
                     </note>
                  
                  
                  
